    people_per_van = 8 # 8 people in each van
    people_in_vans = num_vans * people_per_van

    # L2
    num_buses = 10 # 10 buses
    people_per_bus = 27 # 27 people on each bus
    people_in_buses = num_buses * people_per_bus

    # L3

    # FA

    return answer
